&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Tyres&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Btwin Resist 1 (700x25) used for approximately 1,550 Kms.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Tyres&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Michelin Pro 4 Endurance (700x25) used for approximately 525 Kms. Bike sold.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Pedals&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Shimano PD-M540. (MTB Clipless Pedals)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Brake Pads&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Kool Stop Bicycle Brake Pads with X Pad (Dura-Ace/Ultegra)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Cycling Computer&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Lixada Wireless Cycling Bicycle Computer Bike Computer Multi-Function LED Display Waterproof Odometer Speedometer Cadence LCD 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.aliexpress.com/item/32716626923.html?spm=a2g0s.9042311.0.0.27424c4dpjtsIO&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Frame Top Tube Bag&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;ROSWHEEL bicycle bag front frame top tube bag cycling bags accessories waterproof anti skid BOTTOM UPPER TUBE BAG.
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.aliexpress.com/item/32832946780.html?spm=a2g0s.9042311.0.0.27424c4dQTrk0k&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Lights&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Cycloving LED Bicycle light Bike lights Floodlight 85degree and Meilan x6 Bike rear light 6Modes rechargeable waterproof. 
&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.aliexpress.com/item/32812163767.html?spm=a2g0s.9042311.0.0.27424c4dQTrk0k&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Link&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Hand Pump&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;BTWIN 920 Telescopic Bike Hand Pump With Pressure Gauge.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Bottle Mount&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;BTWIN Universal Bottle Cage Mount.&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
